Package: rrchecklist
Type: Package
Title: Reliable Research Practices Checklist
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jason", "Pither", email = "pitherj@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Mathew", "Vis-Dunbar", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides two checklists for reliable research practices in both
    R Markdown and Quarto formats: evaluating primary research and documenting reliable
    research practices. Checklists cover study planning, conducting research, reporting
    findings, and enhancing transparency. Researchers can complete checklists and render
    to PDF or HTML for submission alongside manuscripts during peer review.
